	<li>Tool to navigate all available patterns</li><li>Playground to learn how the system works and explore new possibilities</li><li>Rapid prototyping tool for creating layouts in HTML</li>
</ul>`
    &segment_type=``
	&padding=`regular`
    &alignment=``
]]

